parameters:
Yeah... I've sent everything I need, so I haven't forgotten
anything.

Momone... I'm really sorry... for being assigned at a time
like this...
It can't be helped... It's for work...
But... maybe I should go with you...
Momone, you have work too, right?

Besides, they say that completing this assignment could lead
to a promotion...

Considering we'll be starting a family soon, I think it's
better to accept this assignment.
But... if I can't see Takkun...

And... we can't have sex... maybe we won't be able to start
a family after all...
I'll come back on the weekends, so let's do it then?
Eh!! You can come back on the weekends!?

Yeah... It's not close, but it's not so far that I can't
come back.
So I can come back on the weekends!!
I'll be back by Friday night.♪
I thought you wouldn't be able to come back at all...
It's not like I'm being assigned overseas.♪

I feel bad for putting the burden on you, Momone, but I'm
counting on you to take care of the house while I'm away.
And so, as a newlywed... I, Momone Onodera...

sent off my husband, Takuya Onodera, and began living
alone...

Ahh... Tak-kun... you can't... you shouldn't lick such a
dirty place...
Tak-kun... I love you so much too...
It's too lonely only being able to meet on weekends!

Could it be... Tak-kun came back because he forgot
something?

That's so mean... Your cute little sister came all this way
to celebrate for you~
Whether you're cute or not depends on the matter at hand.
Then I guess I'm on the cute side♪
Since you're here, why not come in for some coffee?

Ah... no, I'm fine here. I don't plan on staying long
anyway.
I'm not a child anymore, of course I eat properly.
If Akane skips, I get scolded by dad and mom...
I'm fine♪ I'm doing just enough not to get scolded♪

Not just enough to avoid getting scolded, do it properly
like everyone else.
By the way... are you alone? Where's your brother?
Work? But today is his day off, right?

He said there was preparation to do for his new post, so he
left right after putting away the moving boxes...

Ah... now that you mention it, he did say something like
that...

Sister... could it be... were you doing it alone until just
now?
What are you talking about!! There's no way I would do that!
Ahhhn! Takuya-san! I want to have sex with Takuya-san!!
Ha... Haa!? I'm not doing anything!

This girl suddenly comes over and starts saying who knows
what...

I thought I'd give you this as a housewarming gift for
moving here...

I thought you might get lonely by yourself, so I bought some
side dishes for meals from Neko-oka Shopping Street♪

Why would you think I'd get lonely and buy side dishes for
meals...

A woman living alone tends to have an unbalanced diet,
right?
Muu~... I can manage that much myself!
Nnmooh! Don't make fun of your sister!

You should be more considerate of a heartbroken newlywed
living away from her beloved husband

Ah... And while I'm at it, I've also included some household
goods for you to use♪

I'm not worried about the goods... but are the food items
still within their expiration date?

No problem♪ No problem♪ They won't give you a stomachache if
you eat them♪
Akane... you brought leftovers from home, didn't you?
It's a waste to throw them away, right?
Well then♪ Good luck with your solo newlywed life♪
Nnmooh... what did that girl even come here for...

You have to protect the place where Takkun, who is working
hard, comes back to!

Alright! I'll sleep well tonight and start working hard from
tomorrow too!
And then... there's the weekend sex with Takkun♪
